{"id":483,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":85,"title":"85. Smoking","subtitle":"","level":"B1","parts":13,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/85-smoking.483/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/85-smoking-2022-03-07-21-32-40/0-85-smoking.mp3","transcript":"Do you smoke? I've never known that.\nWhen did you start smoking?\nI started smoking when I was eighteen.\nSo, how long have you been a smoker?\nI've smoked for twenty years.\nHow many cigarettes do you smoke a day?\nI smoke two packs of cigarettes a day.\nHave you ever tried to quit?\nYes, I have quit twice: once when I was expecting my baby, Paul,\nand the other time when I had a bad sore throat.\nBut I had a hard time.\nIf you knew what it was doing to your lungs,\nyou would think twice about it!","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:49:05","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Do you smoke? I've never known that.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/85-smoking-2022-03-07-21-32-40/1.mp3","time_start":2.19,"time_end":4.68},{"position":2,"content":"When did you start smoking?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/85-smoking-2022-03-07-21-32-40/2.mp3","time_start":4.79,"time_end":6.24},{"position":3,"content":"I started smoking when I was eighteen.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/85-smoking-2022-03-07-21-32-40/3.mp3","time_start":6.24,"time_end":8.28},{"position":4,"content":"So, how long have you been a smoker?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/85-smoking-2022-03-07-21-32-40/4.mp3","time_start":8.36,"time_end":10.26},{"position":5,"content":"I've smoked for twenty years.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/85-smoking-2022-03-07-21-32-40/5.mp3","time_start":10.26,"time_end":12.3},{"position":6,"content":"How many cigarettes do you smoke a day?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/85-smoking-2022-03-07-21-32-40/6.mp3","time_start":12.4,"time_end":14.73},{"position":7,"content":"I smoke two packs of cigarettes a day.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/85-smoking-2022-03-07-21-32-40/7.mp3","time_start":14.73,"time_end":16.78},{"position":8,"content":"Have you ever tried to quit?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/85-smoking-2022-03-07-21-32-40/8-2022-03-10-11-53-09.mp3","time_start":16.99,"time_end":18.55},{"position":9,"content":"Yes, I have quit twice: once when I was expecting my baby, Paul,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/85-smoking-2022-03-07-21-32-40/9-2022-03-10-11-53-18.mp3","time_start":18.55,"time_end":22.74},{"position":10,"content":"and the other time when I had a bad sore throat.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/85-smoking-2022-03-07-21-32-40/10.mp3","time_start":22.74,"time_end":25.11},{"position":11,"content":"But I had a hard time.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/85-smoking-2022-03-07-21-32-40/11.mp3","time_start":25.2,"time_end":26.53},{"position":12,"content":"If you knew what it was doing to your lungs,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/85-smoking-2022-03-07-21-32-40/12.mp3","time_start":26.53,"time_end":28.96},{"position":13,"content":"you would think twice about it!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/85-smoking-2022-03-07-21-32-40/13.mp3","time_start":29.04,"time_end":30.7}]}